---
import { legalIcons } from '../../utils/data';
---

<section id="privacy-policy" class="py-16 min-h-screen" style="display: none;">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-24 max-w-screen-md">
    <button id="back-to-main" class="mb-8 text-[#a3a3a3] hover:text-[#9C8260] transition">
      ← Back to Home
    </button>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 my-8" />
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">This Privacy Policy is issued by <strong class="font-bold">Kuaru Studios LLC</strong> (“Company”, “we”, or “our”) and applies to the use of our websites and services, including but not limited to our official site and any future platforms (collectively referred to as “this Website”).</p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with applicable data protection laws and this Privacy Policy. We collect, process, and use your personal data to provide and improve our services, and ensure your rights are respected and protected.</p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">If you do not agree to all or part of this Privacy Policy, please discontinue your use of this Website and its services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Scope of This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">This Privacy Policy applies solely to the Site operated by <strong class="font-bold">Kuaru Studios LLC</strong>. It does not extend to any third-party platforms, services, or websites that may be linked from our Site. These third-party services are governed by their own privacy policies, which we do not control or assume responsibility for.</p>


    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">We may collect and store the following personal information when you interact with our services:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
      <li>Identifiable Information: such as name, email address, shipping address, phone number</li>
      <li>Transactional Information: including order details and payment preferences (processed by third-party payment processors)</li>
      <li>Communication Records: such as emails or contact form submissions</li>
      <li>Automatically Collected Information: such as IP address, browser type, usage behavior via cookies (see section 5)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">We do not collect sensitive personal data (e.g., biometric or financial account details) directly.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We use your personal information to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
      <li>Fulfill and ship your orders</li>
      <li>Provide customer support</li>
      <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
      <li>Comply with legal requirements</li>
      <li>Analyze customer data to improve product selection, identify trends, and enhance user experience</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">We do not sell your data. Your information may be shared only with trusted service providers (e.g., logistics or payment platforms) for purposes strictly necessary to perform our services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">Your information will be retained only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Typically:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
      <li>Order-related data: retained for up to 7 years (for accounting and legal compliance)</li>
      <li>Contact or inquiry data: retained for up to 1 year</li>
      <li>Cookies: retention varies by type (see section 5)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">We may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance site functionality, remember your preferences, and analyze usage patterns. You can disable cookies via your browser settings, but doing so may affect the usability of some features.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Protection of Personal Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">We implement reasonable technical and organizational safeguards to protect your information from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, as with all online activity, absolute security cannot be guaranteed.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">Our services are not directed toward children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us. We will promptly delete the information from our records.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">8. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">Depending on your region, you may have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
      <li>Access the data we hold about you</li>
      <li>Request correction or deletion of your personal data</li>
      <li>Object to or restrict processing</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time (where applicable)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">To exercise your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@kuarustudios.com" class="text-[#4c4f45] underline hover:underline">hello@kuarustudios.com</a></p></p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes via the Site or through email, where applicable. Continued use of the Site after changes indicates acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-justify">If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, you may reach us at:</p>
    <p class="mb-4 font-bold text-justify">Kuaru Studios LLC</p>
    <p><span set:html={legalIcons.email} class="text-[#4c4f45]"></span> Email: <a href="mailto:hello@kuarustudios.com" class="text-[#4c4f45] underline hover:underline">hello@kuarustudios.com</a></p>
    <p><span set:html={legalIcons.website} class="text-[#4c4f45]"></span> Website: <a href="https://kuarustudios.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#4c4f45] underline hover:underline">https://kuarustudios.com</a></p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Add scroll to top button -->
  <button id="scroll-to-top" class="fixed bottom-24 right-8 bg-[#a3a3a3] text-white p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-[#9C8260] transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 invisible z-[9999]">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 10l7-7m0 0l7 7m-7-7v18" />
    </svg>
  </button>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const backButton = document.getElementById('back-to-main');
    const privacySection = document.getElementById('privacy-policy');
    const mainContent = document.querySelector('main');
    const scrollToTopButton = document.getElementById('scroll-to-top');

    if (backButton && privacySection && mainContent) {
      backButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
        // 使用淡出淡入效果切換頁面
        if (window.switchToPage) {
          // 先淡出當前頁面，然後淡入主頁面
          window.switchToPage(mainContent, [privacySection]);
        } else {
          // 如果 switchToPage 函數不存在，使用備用方案
        privacySection.style.display = 'none';
        mainContent.style.display = 'block';
        }
        window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
        window.history.pushState({}, '', '/');
        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('privacyPageStateChange', { detail: { isPrivacyPage: false } }));
      });
    }

    // Handle scroll to top button
    if (scrollToTopButton) {
      // Listen for scroll events
      window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
        if (window.scrollY > 300) {
          scrollToTopButton.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'invisible');
          scrollToTopButton.classList.add('opacity-100', 'visible');
        } else {
          scrollToTopButton.classList.add('opacity-0', 'invisible');
          scrollToTopButton.classList.remove('opacity-100', 'visible');
        }
      });

      // Click to scroll to top
      scrollToTopButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
        window.scrollTo({
          top: 0,
          behavior: 'smooth'
        });
      });
    }
  });
</script> 